    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 13th level, your medical knowledge allows you to find a weak point in a creature's chakra network. When you make an attack with your Chakra Scalpel you can treat the target as Vulnerable to the damage. You can activate this ability after you roll the dice but before the outcome of the attack is determined.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Intelligence modifier, and regain all expended uses on a long rest.</p>",
